HEADWORD: Underproportioned
<hw>Un`der*pro*por"tioned</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of
inadequate or inferior proportions; small; poor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

